column5: WOW! very nice wtg!
VN!!!

Two VERY FINE crappie.  You two should be proud of yerslefs.

nice fish.  great background.  lol.  I would have done the mosaic pattern instead, it allows the others to kind of think they know your spot.  lol! I actually have a pic of a 21" crappie of my own but nobody believes me that it is 21" so I won't post it.
Post it ,..I will believe
Nice one Dawg,  Still looks kinds warm down there.  good job on chucking it back.
Post it and let us decide how believable it is.
Very nice, what a horse. WTG
Got out for a few hours yesterday and nabbed this slab!  She was released after a quick pic.
My goodness! That is perty.

Excellent Glen.... that's a beauty slab for sure  Is this the biggest you've caught???  Certainly the biggest I've ever seen Good on you for releasing it  Keep up the good work!!! and thanks for sharing Jacques
My my that is a goddun bud!!  Good on ya for not bunking her too..
WOW nice! Iv never seen a pan fish that big! way to go, and awesome that you let it go!
Way to go Dawgy!  YEEEEEEEEEHAAAAAAAAAAAAAWWWWWWWWWWWWW!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!  Way to protect the genes!
